net.proteusframework.users.audit

Interface PrincipalAuditable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Auditable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FullyAuditable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAuditableEntity, FullyAuditableImpl, Principal, Role

    public interface PrincipalAuditable
extends Auditable
    Implementors wish to have the create and modification user's persisted. The management of the persistences of this property is done using a hibernate listener and is therefore not managed by the application code.
    Author:
    Ken Logan (ken@i2rd.com)
